			<item>
				<title>Lunch &amp; drop in yoga</title>
				<link>https://www.boosterconf.no/2026/program/wednesday/8_lunch/</link>
				<pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>https://www.boosterconf.no/2026/program/wednesday/8_lunch/</guid>
				<description>&lt;p&gt;Time to fill up on energy and discuss the day so far!&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Enjoy our massive buffet both hot and cold with all kinds of cuisines, styles and desserts for days! Vegan options for both too.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Don&amp;rsquo;t forget Booster has 100 speakers (yes really) and they all love to talk to strangers, so don&amp;rsquo;t be afraid to approach someone you don&amp;rsquo;t know and discuss IT.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Need to move around a bit after all the talks and before the food coma hits? Join our daily yoga session the first 30 minutes of every lunch at Dræggen 3.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
