			<item>
				<title>Conference dinner</title>
				<link>https://www.boosterconf.no/2026/program/wednesday/13_conference_dinner/</link>
				<pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>https://www.boosterconf.no/2026/program/wednesday/13_conference_dinner/</guid>
				<description>&lt;p&gt;You are all invited to the conference dinner at Kulturhuset. Bring your conference badge, as this is your ticket. There is no dress code, so come as you are! 😄&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Kulturhuset&amp;rsquo;s address is: Vaskerelven 8, 5014 Bergen. Look it up on &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.openstreetmap.org/directions?engine=fossgis_osrm_foot&amp;amp;route=60.397852%2C5.322499%3B60.391402%2C5.321364#map=16/60.39456/5.32346&#34;&gt;OpenStreetMap&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.google.com/maps/dir/Radisson+Blu+Royal+Hotel,+Bergen,+Dreggsallmenningen+1,+5003+Bergen/Kulturhuset+i+Bergen,+Vaskerelven+8,+5014+Bergen/@60.3941903,5.3184697,16z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m14!4m13!1m5!1m1!1s0x463cfea794f3e3f3:0xb51c2d400a34fa45!2m2!1d5.322817!2d60.3978642!1m5!1m1!1s0x463cfd1ddf784b49:0x607bf5ac1f838ccd!2m2!1d5.3213859!2d60.3914057!3e2?entry=ttu&amp;amp;g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDMwNC4xIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D&#34;&gt;Google Maps&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Do you have any allergies, intolerances or dietary restrictions? Submit them &lt;a href=&#34;https://forms.gle/fHGVUJEsb4FmWaBq8&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; before 6th of March.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
